---
title: Carb Smart Sweet Potato, Chicken Tenders and Goat Cheese Salad with Lentils and Pepitas
description: This hearty and low-starch salad is delicious hot, cold or at room temperature! Rich goat cheese, hearty chicken and wholesome lentils pack each bite with delicious protein.
